OL,3,CWoman in wheelchair 'trapped' at home
OL,4,Cfor two weeks after lift breaks again
OL,6,FThe broken lift makes the stairs
OL,7,Finaccessible for residents in
OL,8,Fwheelchairs
OL,10,FRona O'Donnell has lived independently
OL,11,Fin a supported living block in the
OL,12,Fcentre of Exeter for the last ten
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FRona told us she values that
OL,16,Findependence and has a busy social
OL,17,Flife, but for the last two weeks, she
OL,18,Fhas been trapped inside her own home.
