OL,3,CWoman in wheelchair 'trapped' at home
OL,4,Cfor two weeks after lift breaks again
OL,6,FThe lift that allows her to descend
OL,7,Fthe steps to the street has been
OL,8,Fbroken for the last two weeks.
OL,10,F"I feel isolated," she told ITV News
OL,11,FWest Country.
OL,13,FThis isn't the first time Rona has
OL,14,Ffelt trapped here. We first visited
OL,15,Fher in 2019, when the reliability of
OL,16,Fthe lift had already been an issue
OL,17,Fbefore. The lift has broken down a
OL,18,Fnumber of times since, she told us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
