OL,3,CWoman in wheelchair 'trapped' at home
OL,4,Cfor two weeks after lift breaks again
OL,6,FThis time, the isolation is even
OL,7,Fharder to take. Rona had plans to go
OL,8,Fto the cinema with her friends for her
OL,9,Fbirthday, but had to cancel the trip
OL,10,Fafter she was unable to leave her home.
OL,12,FExeter charity community, equality,
OL,13,Fdisability action (CEDA) says Rona's
OL,14,Fvoice needs to be better heard.
OL,16,FCraig Bowden from CEDA said: "It must
OL,17,Ffeel like being a prisoner in your own
OL,18,Fhome."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
