OL,3,CWoman in wheelchair 'trapped' at home
OL,4,Cfor two weeks after lift breaks again
OL,6,FHe explained: "When it is something as
OL,7,Fsimple as an access issue - you're
OL,8,Fliving in somewhere that is purposely
OL,9,Fadapted for a wheelchair user and then
OL,10,Fone component is broken for such a
OL,11,Flong time - it really does affect your
OL,12,Fhealth and wellbeing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
