OL,3,CWoman in wheelchair 'trapped' at home
OL,4,Cfor two weeks after lift breaks again
OL,6,FHe suggested that a permanent ramp
OL,7,Fshould be installed for the residents,
OL,8,Fadding: "The grief that this one
OL,9,Fsituation has given Rona and the other
OL,10,Fpeople within this establishment over
OL,11,Fthe five, six years that it has
OL,12,Fcontinued to happen could have been
OL,13,Ffixed with a ramp that doesn't require
OL,14,Fany moving parts."
OL,16,FITV News West Country has contacted
OL,17,Faccommodation provider Inclusion
OL,18,FHousing for a comment.
